title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Italy -  Place Moulin Dam
description:
In this video we will fly over the Place Moulin Dam. Place Moulin Dam is one of the largest dams in Europe and is in Bionaz, in Northern Italy. The 678 m long and 155 m high arch dam was constructed between 1955 and 1965 and has an artificial reservoir capable of holding 105 million sq m of water.

It has been declared a Natural Monument by the regional Ministry for the Environment of the Xunta de Galicia.
